ks.framework.sipc
Class Listener

java.lang.Object
  ks.framework.common.network.SimpleServerConnection
      ks.framework.sipc.Listener
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.lang.Cloneable, java.lang.Runnable
public class Listener
extends SimpleServerConnection

The Listener class is responsible for processing all Client requests. Each request is a serialized Command object which is read from the client socket connection.

Author:
George T. Heineman (heineman@cs.wpi.edu)
